"{\"uid\": \"pennlive.com-tv-2024-08-how-to-watch-2024-olympics-closing-ceremony-free-live-stream-time-channel.html\", \"text\": \"If you purchase a product through a link on our site, we may receive compensation.  The 2024 Olympics come to an official close Sunday in Paris withthe Closing Ceremony in Stade de Franceto celebrate the '24 Games and look forward to the 2028 Olympics in Los Angeles. The Closing Ceremony is scheduled for 3 p.m. ET (9 p.m. in Paris) withTV coverage on NBCandstreaming on-demand.  2024 OLYMPIC GAMES  Closing Ceremony at a glance  When:Sunday, Aug. 11 at 3 p.m. ET (9 p.m. local)  Where:Stade de France, Paris, France  TV channel:NBC  Live streams:FuboTV (free trial)|SlingTV (low intro rate)|DirecTV Stream (free trial)|Peacock ($7.99+ per month)  Whispers of surprises are circulating about potential musical acts and entertainers who could perform at the 2024 Olympics Closing Ceremony, and the Paris 2024 Olympic Committee announced \\\"over a hundred\\\" performers will take part in it. Thomas Jolly, who planned the Opening Ceremony that caused a social media stir in the U.S., also planned the closing . Swimmer Katie Ledecky and rower Nick Mead will be flag bearers for the USA.  On the TV side, NBC's Mike Tirico will host the Closing Ceremony alongside Jimmy Fallon, Terry Gannon, Tara Lipinski and Johnny Weir. The ceremony in Paris will also feature the city handover from Paris to Los Angeles, which will host the 2028 Olympics.  SEE ALSO: Team USA gear:Fanatics|Ralph Lauren|Walmart|USA Basketball gear  Olympics TV and streaming:More on Peacock's Gold Zone|Alex Cooper to host interactive watch parties  The 2024 Olympics Closing Ceremony is set for a 3 p.m. ET start on NBC. Live streams are available fromFuboTV (free trial),SlingTV (low intro rate)andDirecTV Stream (free trial).  Use of and/or registration on any portion of this site constitutes acceptance of ourUser Agreement, (updated 8/1/2024) and acknowledgement of ourPrivacy Policy,andYour Privacy Choices and Rights(updated 10/1/2025).  \\u00a92025Advance Local Media LLC. All rights reserved (About Us).The material on this site may not be reproduced, distributed, transmitted, cached or otherwise used, except with the prior written permission of Advance Local.  Community Rulesapply to all content you upload or otherwise submit to this site.  YouTube's privacy policyis availablehereandYouTube's terms of serviceis availablehere.  Ad Choices\"}"